#: ../../../source/Tutorials/Beginner-CLI-Tools/Understanding-ROS2-Topics/Understanding-ROS2-Topics.rst:290
msgid ""
"Finally, you can run ``echo`` on the ``pose`` topic and recheck rqt_graph:"
msgstr ""

