msgid ""
"ros2 topic pub /pose geometry_msgs/msg/PoseStamped '{header: \"auto\", pose: "
"{position: {x: 1.0, y: 2.0, z: 3.0}}}'"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/Tutorials/Beginner-CLI-Tools/Understanding-ROS2-Topics/Understanding-ROS2-Topics.rst:307
msgid ""
"If the message does not use a full header, but just has a field with type "
"``builtin_interfaces/msg/Time``, that can be set to the value ``now``."
